Sampling from a distribution
========================================================

Normal distribution
```{r,eval=F}
rnorm(n = number of observations,
      mean = vector of means,
      sd = vector of means)
```

Sampling from a distribution
========================================================

Normal distribution
```{r}
sample_norm <- rnorm(n = 10000,
                     mean = 10,
                     sd = 1)
hist(sample_norm)
```

