Solution
========================================================

1.
```{r}
require(ggplot2)
p <- qplot(data=experiment1,
           x=factorA,
           y=response,
           colour=factorB,
           geom="boxplot")
print(p)
```

Solution
========================================================

2.
```{r}
fit <- aov(data = experiment1,
           response~factorA*factorB)
summary(fit)
plot(fit)
```

